<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,874,1223]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,219,874,899]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Body.</emphasis>
Ocellus on anterior margin or slightly below anterior margin. Frontoclypeus not tumid, clypeal sulcus prominent. Forewing usually with three anteapical cells, inner anteapical cell open basally.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="106" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,874,1223]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,267,946,971]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Male.</emphasis>
Pygofer side with short tooth on apical half near ventral margin. Segment X long, sclerotized dorsally and laterally. Valve long, triangular. Style preapical angle distinct. Connective Y-shaped or H-shaped. Aedeagus base triangular, shaft strongly curved dorso-anteriorly.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,491,1054,1079]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,874,1223]" box="[199,491,1054,1079]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1054,1079]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Distribution.</emphasis>
Worldwide.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="106" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,874,1223]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1090,1115]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species of this genus are a very homogenous assemblage and have been placed in various genera at one time or another based on external appearance, including the five genera synonymised here, i.e., 
<emphasis box="[1381,1435,1127,1150]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Arya</emphasis>
Distant, 
<taxonomicName authority="Distant" authorityName="Distant" box="[253,440,1162,1187]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Bituitus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[253,340,1164,1187]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Bituitus</emphasis>
Distant
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Distant" authorityName="Distant" box="[458,678,1162,1187]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Nandidrug" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[458,580,1162,1187]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Nandidrug</emphasis>
Distant
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Distant" authorityName="Distant" box="[697,914,1162,1187]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Paivanana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[697,818,1164,1187]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Paivanana</emphasis>
Distant
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Distant" authorityName="Distant" box="[984,1219,1162,1187]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Viridomarus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[984,1124,1162,1187]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Viridomarus</emphasis>
Distant
